{"id":16,"parent_id":0,"book_id":22563,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":16,"title":"The Transfiguration of Christ","subtitle":"","short_title":14,"uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ","content":[["div",{"id":"head1","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.head1"},[".titleNumber","14"],["h1","The Transfiguration of Christ"]],[".bodyBlock",[".topic",["h2","Theme"],["div",{"id":"p4","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p4"},"On the Mount of Transfiguration Peter, James, and John beheld the glory of Jesus Christ and received keys of priesthood from holy visitations. These keys still reside in the Church."]],[".topic",["h2","Theme Analysis"],["div",{"id":"f1","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.f1"},["ul.content-list alphaCaps",["li",["span.label","A."],["div",[".para","The transfiguration of Christ and those events surrounding it were an important witness to Peter, James, and John of the divinity of Christ and the reality of revelation."]]],["li",["span.label","B."],["div",[".para","A significant part of the transfiguration experience was the committal of priesthood keys to the presiding apostles"]]],["li",["span.label","C."],["div",[".para","Priesthood keys, in essence, are the power of presiding over and conducting the activities of the priesthood of the Church"]]],["li",["span.label","D."],["div",[".para","All the priesthood keys presently pertaining to mortality are held by the President of the Church."]]]]]],[".topic",["h2","Study Sources"],[".topic",["h3","New Testament Reading Assignment"],["div",{"id":"p12","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p12"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/16"},"Matthew 16, through 18"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/8.11-38"},"Mark 8:11-38"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/9"},"9"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/9.15-50"},"Luke 9:18-50"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/10.1-16"},"10:1-16"],"."]],[".topic",["h3","Course Manual"],["div",{"id":"p14","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p14"},"Chapter 14, “The Transfiguration of Christ”"]],[".topic",["h3","Standard Works"],["div",{"id":"p16","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p16"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.1-9"},"Matthew 17:1-9"],". What happened on the Mount of Transfiguration?"],["div",{"id":"p17","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p17"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.20,21"},"D&C 63:20, 21"],". What else occurred on the occasion of the transfiguration?"],["div",{"id":"p18","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p18"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/9.28-36"},"Luke 9:28-36"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/2-ne/1.16-19"},"2 Peter 1:16-19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/28.13-17"},"3 Nephi 28:13-17"],". Further light on what transfiguration is."],["div",{"id":"p19","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p19"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/16.16-19"},"Matthew 16:16-19"],". How did the Savior describe the use of priesthood keys?"],["div",{"id":"p20","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p20"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/81.2"},"D&C 81:2"],". Who always has the right to the keys of the kingdom?"],["div",{"id":"p21","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p21"},["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.12,13"},"D&C 27:12, 13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.11-16"},"110:11-16"],". How and by whom were priesthood keys given to the leaders of the present dispensation?"]],[".topic",["h3","Basic Library"],["div",{"id":"p23","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p23"},["span.emphasis","Jesus the Christ,"],"pp. 370-77. The transfiguration."],["div",{"id":"p24","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p24"},["span.emphasis","Gos. Doc.,"],"p. 136. What are priesthood keys?"],["div",{"id":"p25","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p25"},["span.emphasis","DS,"],"3:125-30. The restoration of priesthood keys."],["div",{"id":"p26","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p26"},"Joseph Fielding Smith in",["span.emphasis","CR,"],"Apr. 1972, pp. 98-99. The keys of the priesthood are in the Church today."]],[".topic",["h3","Additional Sources"],["div",{"id":"p28","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p28"},"Bruce R. McConkie,",["span.emphasis","Doctrinal New Testament Commentary,"],"1:399-400."],["div",{"id":"p29","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p29"},"Bruce R. McConkie,",["span.emphasis","Mormon Doctrine,"],"pp. 411-13. The keys of the kingdom."]]],[".topic",["h2","Some Suggestions for Presentation"],[".subtitle","(Ideas Other Teachers Have Used)"],[".topic",["h3","Priesthood and Keys (A Discussion)"],["div",{"id":"p33","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p33"},"To help students understand how keys relate to priesthood, the teacher might give the example of a father giving a son a new car. Ask what would be needed to make the car run? (Keys.) How do keys help the priesthood function? Is there often more than one key for a car? Why? Why must there be many priesthood keys? (See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.21"},"D&C 128:21"],".)"]],[".topic",["h3","Revelation—the Rock upon Which the Church Is Built (An Illustration)"],["div",{"id":"p35","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p35"},"The instructor could place the following statement on the board or on a student handout:"],["div",{"id":"p36","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p36"},"“… Jesus in His teaching says, Upon this rock I will build my Church, and the gates of hell shall not prevail against it. What rock? Revelation.” (Joseph Smith,",["span.emphasis","Teachings,"],"p. 274.)"],["div",{"id":"p37","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p37"},"Then by use of the following analogy, an important point about revelation could be made:"],[".",{"id":"f2","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.f2"}],["div",{"id":"p44","uri":"/manual/the-life-and-teachings-of-jesus-and-his-apostles-instructors-guide-rel-211-12/the-transfiguration-of-christ.p44"},"Who is the one through whom revelation for the Church is given? (See",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/107.91,92"},"D&C 107:91, 92"],". Note also",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/1.42"},"John 1:42"],", Inspired Version.)"]]]]],"refs":null}
